==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Lactifuge
<hw>Lac"ti*fuge</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>lac</ets>, <ets>lactis</ets>, milk + <ets>fugare</ets> to
expel.]</ety> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>A medicine to check the secretion
of milk, or to dispel a supposed accumulation of milk in any part of the
body.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lactim</ent>⟦br⟧
